title: Ep. 5 - Mr. Beast Roasts Ludwig's YouTube
description: We didn't call him out on it, but for some reason Ludwig kept saying "it's lit" this episode. The boys take the time to discuss cheating in school (allegedly), erections on planes, and whether or not Justin Long would beat Slime in a fight.
